WEEK 1 FITNESS JOURNEY RECAP! My man @chadowens2 getting me right!! 💪🏾 If anybody wants some training from him please hit him up! It’s my first time ever having a personal trainer, and I love it!  Feels good to be back in the gym and being consistent! The most tough part about this journey is eating right, but with discipline it can be done! Thanks to my queen @rachaelostovich for pushing me and helping me meal prep haha 😘 Also Mahalo to @ironhawaiianfitness gym!  They got the best equipment and machines 💪🏾 I don’t know where this fitness journey will take me, but I do know that I need this in my life.  Fitness and health is key… and I’m just trying to become a better me! Hopefully this can inspire others to do the same. Cheee! 🤙🏽💪🏾
